<h1>CSC 161 Module on Working with Characters, Strings, and I/O</h1>

<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>
This module introduces CSC 161 students to writing dynamic programs that
can take input and follow commands based on input, including
</p>

<ol>
<li>  characters 
<li>  strings
<li>  input and output.
</ol>

